  "notes": "BRANDING & DESIGN GUIDE\n\nColors:\n  Primary: #14b8a6 (teal)\n  Hover: #0d9488\n  Light: #99f6e4\n  Accents: #fef08a (yellow), #fecdd3 (pink), #a5f3fc (cyan)\n  Text: #334155, Heading: #0f172a, Muted: #64748b\n  Background: #ffffff, Cards: #ffffff\n\nTypography:\n  Font: Inter (Google Fonts, 400-800)\n  H1: 76px weight 800, letter-spacing -0.04em\n  H2: 38px weight 800, letter-spacing -0.03em\n  Body: 15-16px, line-height 1.6\n\nPatterns:\n  Buttons: gradient 135deg #14b8a6 to #0d9488, radius 10px\n  Cards: white bg, 1px border #e4e4e4, radius 16px\n  Shadows: progressive scale (sm, md, lg)\n  Nav: 64px fixed, backdrop-blur 16px\n  Container: max-width 1140px\n  Sections: 100px vertical padding\n\nTone:\n  \"Plan with Storymaps\"\n  \"Open source. Free forever.\"\n  \"No signup required. Works in your browser.\"\n  Direct, benefit-focused, no jargon.\n  Action verbs: Map, Plan, Ship, Share, Export.\n\nDark Mode:\n  Background: #0f172a\n  Cards: #1e293b\n  Border: #2a3a4e"
